---
import BaseHead from '../components/BaseHead.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---

<html>
	<head>
		<BaseHead title="About Coobeeyon Development" description="Custom software development and consulting" />
	</head>
	<body>
		<Header />

		<h1>About Coobeeyon Development</h1>

		<hr>

		<p>
			Coobeeyon Development is a custom software development and consulting
			company based in Toronto, Ontario, Canada. We specialize in building web
			applications, mobile apps, and APIs for businesses of all sizes.

		<p>
			Our team of experienced developers, designers, and project managers work
			closely with our clients to deliver high-quality software solutions that
			meet their unique needs and requirements.

		<p>
			Whether you need help with a new project, an existing application, or
			ongoing support and maintenance, we have the skills and expertise to help
			you succeed.

		<Footer />
	</body>
</html>
